      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12 ">
            <h1 class="text-capitalize">aboutUs</h1>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ipsa rerum reiciendis, corrupti vel enim
              doloremque maxime recusandae deleniti, autem reprehenderit laudantium praesentium ducimus blanditiis
              repudiandae. Quidem quos ex ipsam ipsum?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12 text-center links">
            <h1 class="text-capitalize">navLinks</h1>
            <li><a href="#"> Home </a></li>
            <li><a href="#bengaliid"> Bengali </a></li>
            <li><a href="#hindiid"> Hindi </a></li>
